    <h1>Lunch box your web app.</h1>
    <p>The Bentobox is our conceptual model for understanding web applications and their components.</p>

    <p>The Japanese lunchbox model aims to have a balanced mix of things. Much like web apps, the “Ekiben“, looks for content which is arranged in the most efficient, graceful manner. The bento is presented in a simple, beautiful, balanced way. Nothing lacking. Nothing superfluous. Not decorated, but wonderfully designed.</p>
